{"tid":848403,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】洪欣疑慘受暴虐現醫院 憔悴湊女 自爆多次離家出走","createTime":"2018-10-05T01:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T09:11:50.000Z","uid":48905,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef6fac144392b1ef7d87cc4a409b6a638a29e182","tid":848403,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T01:38:53.000Z","msg":"洪欣星期二（2號）深夜在微博留言話︰「打西女人的男人要不得。」網民擔心她受到家暴。<br />\n<br />\n翌日，有人見她包到冚單拖現身醫院。拎完藥不久，壹仔就碰到她獨自湊女，她在街上邊行邊覆口訊，滿懷心事，非常憔悴。<br />\n<br />\n由於洪欣穿長袖衫和長褲，見不到有否傷痕。但平日素顏都好省鏡的她，這日非常不在狀態，相當憔悴，沒有心機。雖然掛住覆口訊，講到皺眉，但她全程拖實女兒，絕對是盡責媽媽。<br />\n<br />\n雖然當晚隔了兩個鐘，她就急刪留言，更話是一場誤會。但原來一起十三年，二人有不少磨擦，洪欣試過多次離家出走。兩夫婦接受內地節目訪問時，張丹峰說：「記得最嚴重那一次，是在上海吧，她一摔門就走。」<br />\n<br />\n洪欣亦坦言：「剛開始他（張丹峰）會追，現在沒有了。我記得有一次我離家出走，我自己駕車，繞來繞去一兩小時，他都不給我打電話。我回到家裡，我發覺他睡着了。」<br />\n<br />\n張丹峰指洪欣性格火曝，笑說自己受到家暴，「就那種發脾氣很火爆的，自己消下來就好，要不她會動手打人的。夏天去拍戲，我都不敢讓她經常來探我的班，因為夏天穿得少，她喜歡掐人。」<br />\n<br />\n洪欣曾說，婚後兩個人要二位一體去解決問題，要花時間和心力去經營。之前細她十年的張丹峰，跟經理人畢瀅傳緋聞，她都力撐老公。<br />\n<br />\n經歷那麼多風雨，很不容易才走到今日，祝福他們能夠彼此珍惜和包容。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/093730_3a287d2a22c11e3511c2d7866d7895ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F093730_3a287d2a22c11e3511c2d7866d7895ca.png&h=f33edfcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/093738_5c3f5ae72f0175388cdc1ee3b5916300.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F093738_5c3f5ae72f0175388cdc1ee3b5916300.png&h=bf56b5b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/093741_b83ecd437c63368145febc622630664d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F093741_b83ecd437c63368145febc622630664d.png&h=d538e04d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/093744_478c0ab4b32f79a8e79bceae83e90d95.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F093744_478c0ab4b32f79a8e79bceae83e90d95.png&h=54ac6468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/093750_febe7ac842c34e819ea703973a3492ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F093750_febe7ac842c34e819ea703973a3492ee.png&h=1efb71f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/093756_c849ebdfc8ad975dd2f93526a5a25fc3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F093756_c849ebdfc8ad975dd2f93526a5a25fc3.gif&h=db1adcb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/093757_1274bc94944ae850385aa492746e8b46.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F093757_1274bc94944ae850385aa492746e8b46.gif&h=6206f0f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b67c1845826ef7113fa6310c30e7086959fa8ef","tid":848403,"uid":82917,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T01:55:00.000Z","msg":"恭喜你簽左個洪欣咁蠢既。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da0e24811eaa8ddb6f8a1f74f1925ae7c71b030","tid":848403,"uid":42435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"快撚D捧紅佢，佢係我老婆咩，打工仔嚟㗎! 打工仔梗係要擔擔抬抬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01dc820c580cb8a9b335fbebb2a498786c97b39c","tid":848403,"uid":7699,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"repl